{"id": "general-chat--troubleshooting--thank-you-did-you-follow-the-meshtastic", "title": "thank you. did you follow the meshtastic", "forum": "General Chat", "messages": [{"id": "1491821654035402915", "author": "PantsManUK", "author_handle": "pantsmanuk", "user_id": "162564349548953600", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/162564349548953600/91b96d660866556aef697ea519d58ec7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 9, 2026 11:26 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-09 11:26 a.m.", "text": "", "content_html": "", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1491827623851065476", "author": "abbie", "author_handle": "antijingoist", "user_id": "438481015267262466", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/438481015267262466/40d5ba17eeda9f1e7bc3052b737842b0.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 9, 2026 11:50 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-09 11:50 a.m.", "text": "for assembling hardware?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>for assembling hardware?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1491880949179224217", "author": "PantsManUK", "author_handle": "pantsmanuk", "user_id": "162564349548953600", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/162564349548953600/91b96d660866556aef697ea519d58ec7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 9, 2026 3:22 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-09 3:22 p.m.", "text": "Ah... Well, the official Heltec GNSS module comes with a single cable. It only plugs in one way at either end, so it's pretty \"bomb proof\". https://heltec.org/project/l76-gnss-module/", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Ah... Well, the official Heltec GNSS module comes with a single cable. It only plugs in one way at either end, so it&#39;s pretty &quot;bomb proof&quot;.\n\n<a href=\"https://heltec.org/project/l76-gnss-module/\">https://heltec.org/project/l76-gnss-module/</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-author-container><a class=chatlog__embed-author-link href=\"https://heltec.org/author/ashley/\"><div class=chatlog__embed-author>ashley</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=\"https://heltec.org/project/l76-gnss-module/\"><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">L76K GNSS Module</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">L76K is a low-power GNSS positioning module with multi-constellation support. It is fully compatible with WiFi LoRa 32 V4 and Mesh Node T114, making it an ideal choice for projects like Meshtastic.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/P40wAu4Pp19zcZK3ZHnjpGhGbWt40x6nKO8H4_KAk24/https/heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/L76K_B.png> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/P40wAu4Pp19zcZK3ZHnjpGhGbWt40x6nKO8H4_KAk24/https/heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/L76K_B.png alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/L76K_B.png> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}]}